visual.name: scatterRect
visual.description: This visual enables you to visualize your business data into an intelligent scatter plot, based on a X dimension as well as an Y dimension. Design your business rules and implement them into the visual through a simple drag and drop, in order to analyze the performance of your products. Have a better understanding of top performers and low performers among your data thanks to a unique system with 3 customizable zones : good, medium, bad. The position and size of each zone can be different according to each of your products.
